/ 2023 VOLUME #5
Summer time is over and the cold weather comes.
Lush greenery fades along with its tranquil
gentleness. We anticipate rich autumn charm
and colourful scenery.
In the past few months, Beijing Clubhouse launched
a series of themed activities. The brand new
“Master Chef Cooking Class” allows Members to
explore local cuisine and advanced cooking skills;
the “Kids Fun and Learning Workshop” enables
Members’ families to experience the aesthetics of
tea appreciation and the art of colour painting; the
“Mainland Members’ Golf Parent-Child Tournament”
has been revived, allowing players of all ages to
swing for fun.
We have held knowledge-sharing seminars with
different themes, including “Elite Family · Clear
Vision — How to Keep Eyes Young” to guide Members
on eye health practice and “Five Thousand Years of
Chinese Emperors — Study of Qin Shihuang” that
allows Members insights into history. In addition,
we have organised a “Create to Love Workshop” for
Members’ children to create goodwill pony picture
books for Our Learning House.
The “Horse Owner Appreciation Dinner” assembled
connoisseurs to experience the glory of horse
ownership, and to explore the spirit of champions;
the “Journey to Horse Ownership” programme
provided Members with in-depth horse racing
knowledge and the charm of horse racing; the
Greater Bay Area “Journey with Horses Series”
brought new summer project with practical content
in the stable.
Beijing Clubhouse is committed to creating more
inspiring activities for Members around three pillars:
“Horse Connoisseur”, “Social Sophistication” and
“Community Leadership”, to enrich leisure time
and uplift lifestyles. Meanwhile, the new horse
racing season kicked off in September. We look
forward to more mainland horse owners, pursuing
excellence with their beloved horses, and sharing
glorious moments together.
卷首语

HAPPY
REUNION
IN AUTUMN
暄气渐消，暑去寒来，天地褪去葱翠绿意，
沉淀出独有的娴静与温婉。我们感受着
浓浓秋韵，书写下闲适安然的风光图卷。
过去的几个月里，北京会所开展了一系列
别出心裁的主题活动。全新“星厨学堂”
系列活动引领会员探索各地美食，进阶
厨艺；“童趣坊”活动邀请会员家庭体验
茶艺美学和彩绘艺术；“内地会员高尔夫
亲子赛”活力再启，大小球员畅享挥杆
乐趣。
我们举办了不同主题的知识分享会，不仅有
聚焦会员眼健康“菁英家庭清晰视野
如何保持眼睛年轻态”的主题讲座，也有
让会员从历史中收获感悟的“上下五千年
之华夏帝王篇秦始皇”分享会。
此外，我们举办了“童话艺创工作坊”，
带领会员小朋友为仁育苑创作小马绘本，
传递善意与温情。
马主答谢晚宴”凝聚伯乐精英，感受马主
荣耀，探索冠军精神；“赛马全接触”系列
分享会引领会员深入了解赛马知识，感受
马运魅力；大湾区“骏伴好年华”活动
带来全新暑期项目及马房实践内容。
北京会所始于初心，臻于匠心，致力于
围绕“伯乐群英”、“至尊社交”和“聚贤
博善”三大会员价值主张为会员打造更多
精彩纷呈的主题活动，丰富闲暇时光，
乐享格调生活。与此同时，全新马季已于
月燃情开锣，我们期待着更多内地马主
与佳驷携手并进，追求卓越，共迎荣耀
时刻。
潘小莺
北京会所总经理

General Manager,
